Using factual knowledge from KGs to pre-train LLMs has also infused structured knowledge [Moiseev2022SKILLSK]. This integration of KGs with LLMs, along with efficient prompts, has made it convenient to inject world knowledge and incorporate new evolving information into language models [Santos2022KnowledgePI]. Additionally, knowledge expressed in high-resource language KBs has been transferred into LMs tuned for low-resource languages [Zhou2021PrixLMPF, Liu2021LearningDR].